{"tid":211221,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊數最賤格既ex分手後做過啲咩","createTime":"2017-04-21T13:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T12:01:19.000Z","uid":97538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"443a0483c6944f1f7f636997a32f378d05ce484d","tid":211221,"uid":97538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"前度呢樣野真係反轉豬肚就係屎<br />\n我ex係同事 分手之後當我係觀音兵咁<br />\n呼之則來 揮之則去<br />\n佢知道我受唔住佢嗲我<br />\n一有野叫我幫手就係度賣晒屎忽咁嗲我<br />\n佢做錯野 就係咁推個責任落我度<br />\n係老闆面前搵藉口拉我落水 <br />\n到我做野出事 其他同事都好關心 佢就冷眼旁觀<br />\n仆街啦賤男<br />\n利申：藍絲，not hehe post<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊分享下最賤格嘅前度係可以做得出啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0646433afe0e77dc41440f1eeb5f563c1b83b7","tid":211221,"uid":34912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"打電話黎叫我用員工優惠幫佢買電腦"},{"pid":"fb83c2897a856053ab1df6a5e292b4779d29e102","tid":211221,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"周圍同人講我有情緒病 中傷我 話我痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b37201808b5f1e2244dda3808840ed4e9416b1","tid":211221,"uid":5047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"同我講佢仲愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e065706d8fa94889ed0edf56d2b20ec182580f9","tid":211221,"uid":12717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"Hurt完我話想復合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab5c6252